text: This obsoletes IRM 2.14.1, Asset Management, Information Technology (IT) Asset Management.

The material in IRM 2.14.1, Asset Management, Information Technology (IT) Asset Management is obsolete because it’s being replaced by several sections under new IRM chapter 2.149, IT Asset Management.
All employees Enterprise-wide responsible for managing IT equipment, including Asset Management’s customers, asset owners, contractors and vendors.
